  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678910/extras/79512f78e4764a8fd3b9cfe3669634ae.poster.avif?t=1721969676\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678910/extras/79512f78e4764a8fd3b9cfe3669634ae.webm?t=1721969676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678910/extras/79512f78e4764a8fd3b9cfe3669634ae.mp4?t=1721969676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Mermaid Tale is an exploration adventure game where you play as Kaya, a young mermaid who wants to help her best friend! <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>How is Shimmering Shampoo made? <br></li><li>What are the nine keys? <br></li><li>Where are the gems of the night? <br><br>Along with the other mermaids, there are various tasks waiting for you to complete in order for this forgotten magic to fulfill its mission.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678910/extras/c8687e3748e334d31ad7fc6c6e6b7b7c.poster.avif?t=1721969676\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678910/extras/c8687e3748e334d31ad7fc6c6e6b7b7c.webm?t=1721969676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678910/extras/c8687e3748e334d31ad7fc6c6e6b7b7c.mp4?t=1721969676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul></li><li>Explore all the areas around the ancient amphitheater!<br></li><li>Chat with the other mermaids who want to help too!<br></li><li>Help prepare everything needed for your friend and this forgotten place!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678910/extras/f4b99a7c8a6a988891e0157ec6f617a9.poster.avif?t=1721969676\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678910/extras/f4b99a7c8a6a988891e0157ec6f617a9.webm?t=1721969676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678910/extras/f4b99a7c8a6a988891e0157ec6f617a9.mp4?t=1721969676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul>",
